OL,3,CJersey man used 'specifically adapted
OL,4,Cphone case' to covertly film women
OL,6,FA Jersey man has been sentenced to six
OL,7,Fmonths in prison for sexually
OL,8,Fmotivated offences.
OL,10,FAndrew Russell Renouf, 36, admitted
OL,11,Ftwo counts of conduct likely to cause
OL,12,Fa breach of the peace and one count of
OL,13,Fa breach of a sex offender restraining
OL,14,Forder.
OL,16,FHe was made subject of the
OL,17,Fnotification requirements on the Sex
OL,18,FOffenders' Register for a minimum of
OL,19,Fseven years.
