OL,3,CJersey man used 'specifically adapted
OL,4,Cphone case' to covertly film women
OL,6,FThe Magistrate's Court heard how he
OL,7,Fused a mobile phone, concealed in a
OL,8,Fspecially adapted case, to covertly
OL,9,Ffilm women in public places around the
OL,10,Fisland.
OL,12,FBy possessing the phone, Renouf was in
OL,13,Fbreach of his sexual offender
OL,14,Frestraining order which had been
OL,15,Fimposed in 2021 for similar offending.
OL,17,FThe crimes were committed for his own
OL,18,Fsexual gratification.
