OL,6,FPolice Constable Jack Maguire, the
OL,7,Finvestigating officer, said: "Tackling
OL,8,Foffending against women and girls is a
OL,9,Fforce priority.
OL,11,F"The States of Jersey Police are
OL,12,Fcommitted to investigating and
OL,13,Fprosecuting all offenders and
OL,14,Fencourage anyone who has been the
OL,15,Fvictim of a crime to report to police
OL,16,For other agencies below who are in a
OL,17,Fposition to offer support and guidance
OL,18,Fthrough all stages of the criminal
OL,19,Fjustice process".
